flowchart LR
    P([Prospect]) --> S1[Stage 1: PITCH]
    S1 -->|yes| S2[Stage 2: CONVERSION]
    S1 -.->|silence| X1([No follow-up])
    S1 -.->|no| X2([Suppressed])
    S2 -->|paid| S3[Stage 3: FIRST EPISODE]
    S3 -->|silence / perfect| S4[Stage 4: STEADY SERVICE]
    S3 -->|swap / pivot| S3
    S4 -->|weekly cycle| S4
    S4 -.->|pause| PA([Paused])
    S4 -.->|stop / churn| R([Revoked])
    PA -.->|resume| S4
